Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mountain Cabin SL"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa? Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, is it you, Sakura? -You've been reminiscing about the past again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pegasus Super Express will be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there is a reserved guest coming for a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash in a Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take a look there. It's a dam construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the upper dam is worn out, this one's getting constructed with emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You are next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamao, what are you going to bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This one. I got this on my birthday from my mom. There's my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The trace of the SL rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chugging through there, puffing smokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chug-chug- Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give us your most precious thing. -I don't have such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one. Your energy capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But that one is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Atom, then show us the inside of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow, is it like this? -Let me see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, show me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-It hurts. It hurts! -Tamao, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We just looked inside Atom's chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this station unmanned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Stations outside cities are mostly unmanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, what is that big construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the old upper dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's included in our field trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cabin we are going to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's of milk cows, the Holsteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you for letting us stay. -No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The SL!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it in the transportation museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's SL? -It's an old steam locomotive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an antique for this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you talk bad about Degoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Degoichi? What's the point of cleaning it? It doesn't even work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you out of your mind? -This one can run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. There's no way this junk is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! What are you... This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That kid disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thunders. -I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard mountain weather is unpredictable, but I didn't expect it to change so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Look at that, Tamao's trembling. -Wow, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coward. It's only a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, it's from the upper part of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The last express is coming in at 7:30 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, go and take a look. -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm will pass by after we sing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing together. Sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm soup is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up. It's not good for your body to not eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, what a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a storm since I was born, for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,30 years? Then you are only 30 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Scary! -Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sakura, switch it to private powering. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sir, what's this? -It's a signal for emergency evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, we are from the cabin in lower region.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dam is about to collapse due to the drainage pump problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate to a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Can you not send us a rescue team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All transportation have stopped. We can't move because of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't care about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's up at its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crack...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go back to the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! There's a problem! There's a crack on the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Atom, what's wrong with your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken for some unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of another...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to evacuate below the constructing dam in downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That new dam will keep us from that fast current even if the upper dam collapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... But how are we going to evacuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We could get into the passenger car of Degoichi outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and Atom could move that to a safe place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible for Atom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If he upholds the passenger car, he wouldn't be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His jet legs are broken now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-My! -I was counting on Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, try operating Degoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You said it can run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Grandpa. Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move this SL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why not? -Explain it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We will all drawn like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not even sure whether the rail is safe or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the railroad bridge is inside tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take care of that by flying in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it still wouldn't work. I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The house in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I don't want to die! I don't want to die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, please? Please save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please operate Degoichi. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single day in which I haven't looked after Degoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always believed that it will run some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's your dream to make Degoichi run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not going to do it, then I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get in Degoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, please take care of the passenger car. I'll be in the engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please get in the passenger car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here. We will get killed if we stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, let's move. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an automated system of Degoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell it simply, I am just a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there was a coal mine near the upper dam,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Degoichi and I transported coal everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but on a stormy day, at the usual curve,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,brake suddenly stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my last run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the owner of this house and the coal mine took us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He remodeled me like this that time. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working in this house since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about Sakura, the grandkid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the inheritor of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Her parents were killed in a plane accident
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even before her first birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've been looking after her since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission is to protect her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a retired one like this, but I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please insert me into Degoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry. We have to do this fast. -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We are finally going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he will take care of it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We are leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We are leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving, moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's done! -It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, it moved. It can run like I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, fly ahead and check the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Good, sir, please hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's life depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The railroad bridge will be in danger if we don't take that tree away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please put forth your energy a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going reviving Degoichi's strength and SL's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job! Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, countercurrent is right behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shall we go check? -I don't want to see it. It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to get caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please! Speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the new dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One more round! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, an uphill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be safe to go up like this. Don't lose your speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We finally shook it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are safe! -Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are safe now. I'm not scared anymore. -Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe thanks to your grandpa. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Retired? No way. You can still do great jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tamao's pendant. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So this is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This got in and must have interfered the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. My energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you did a great job. Now the danger is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break. Put on the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now he can stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is odd. The brake must be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, is it pouring outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. Would you like to take a look outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This brake lever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't move. It's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, the brake is broken. Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The brake? Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work. Gosh, if only I had the energy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The rail is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no path. No path!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying. Flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. What about grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher, are you all right? -Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa was determined to go through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact... Your grandfather was... What should I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a robot. The automated system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lying! Lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way my grandpa was a robot. Lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Grandpa! Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, it seems like we are going to have to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ask Dr. Ochanomizu to fix him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Doctor will fix it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical country of Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Caesar was destroyed after leaving an odd cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What secret does this temple hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dog and scaraboid robots start attacking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work. My energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Cleopatra?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Cleopatra's Mystery." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "Cleopatra's Mystery"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
